evat de Energy Nougat belangrijke allergenen?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"A: Ja, dit is belangrijk om te weten. De basis van de reep bevat amandelen en ei. Afhankelijk van de smaak kunnen er ook andere noten (zoals pistache) of sulfiet in zitten. Raadpleeg altijd de specifieke ingrediëntenlijst op de verpakking als je een allergie hebt.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n<\/script>\n\n<style>\n    \/* CSS voor soepel scrollen *\/\n    html {\n        scroll-behavior: smooth;\n    }\n\n    \/* Algemene styling voor de container *\/\n    .seo-product-description {\n        line-height: 1.6;\n        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n        color: #333;\n    }\n\n    \/* Styling voor witruimte van de content *\/\n    .seo-product-description h2, \n    .seo-product-description h3,\n    .seo-product-description h4 {\n        margin-top: 40px;\n        margin-bottom: 15px;\n        color: #111;\n    }\n    .seo-product-description h2:first-of-type,\n    .seo-product-description .product-summary-box + h3 {\n        margin-top: 40px !important;\n    }\n    .seo-product-description p,\n    .seo-product-description ul,\n    .seo-product-description dl {\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    .seo-product-description ul {\n        list-style-position: inside;\n        padding-left: 10px;\n    }\n    .seo-product-description li {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    \n    \/* Styling voor de Navigatie Box *\/\n    .page-nav-box {\n        background: rgba(217, 255, 54, 0.1);\n        border: 1px solid #d9ff36;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        padding: 15px 25px;\n        margin: 30px 0;\n    }\n    .page-nav-box h4 {\n        margin-top: 0;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        color: #333;\n    }\n    .page-nav-box ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        padding: 0;\n        margin: 0;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        gap: 15px;\n    }\n    .page-nav-box ul li a {\n        text-decoration: none;\n        color: #0056b3;\n        font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .page-nav-box ul li a:hover {\n        text-decoration: underline;\n    }\n\n    \/* Styling voor de 'Voordelen in het Kort' box *\/\n    .product-summary-box {\n        background-color: #f9f9f9;\n        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        margin: 40px 0;\n    }\n    .product-summary-box h3 { margin-top: 0; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px; }\n    .summary-columns { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; }\n    .summary-column { width: 48%; }\n    .summary-column h4 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid; padding-bottom: 5px; }\n    .summary-column.pros h4 { border-color: #28a745; }\n    .summary-column.cons h4 { border-color: #dbb8ff; } \/* Aangepast naar secundaire kleur *\/\n    .summary-column ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }\n    .summary-column ul li { margin-bottom: 8px; }\n\n    \/* Styling voor de voedingstabel *\/\n    .nutrition-table-amacx{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:25px 0;font-size:15px;color:#333;background-color:#fff}.nutrition-table-amacx thead tr{background-color:#f2f2f2;color:#222;text-align:left;font-weight:700}.nutrition-table-amacx th,.nutrition-table-amacx td{padding:12px 15px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8}.nutrition-table-amacx tbody tr{transition:background-color .2s ease}.nutrition-table-amacx tbody tr:nth-child(even){background-color:#f9f9f9}.nutrition-table-amacx tbody tr:hover{background-color:#f1f1f1}.nutrition-table-amacx .sub-item{padding-left:30px;}.nutrition-table-amacx strong{font-weight:600}\n\n    \/* FAQ Styling *\/\n    .faq-list { margin-top: 25px; }\n    .faq-list dt { font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; color: #111; }\n    .faq-list dd { margin-left: 0; margin-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8; color: #555; }\n    .faq-list dd a { color: #0056b3; }\n    .faq-list dd a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n\n    \/* Media Query voor mobiele apparaten *\/\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n        .summary-columns, .page-nav-box ul {\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .summary-column {\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n        .summary-column.cons {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n    }\n<\/style>","text_alignment":"left","add_vertical_spacing":true,"add_horizontal_spacing":true}},"custom_liquid_teda9d":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"Vergelijkingstabel","settings":{"color_scheme":"scheme-2","liquid":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"nl\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Uitgebreide Vergelijking Energierepen<\/title>\n<style>\n    :root {\n        --primary-color: #d9ff36;\n        --secondary-color: #dbb8ff;\n        --text-color: #333;\n        --header-text-color: #111;\n        --border-color: #e0e0e0;\n        --background-light: #ffffff;\n        --background-alt: #f9f9f9;\n    }\n    .comparison-container {\n        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n        color: var(--text-color);\n        margin: 20px auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    .comparison-container h2 {\n        text-align: center;\n        color: var(--header-text-color);\n        margin-bottom: 30px;\n        font-size: 28px;\n    }\n    .comparison-table {\n        width: 100%;\n        border-collapse: collapse;\n        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .comparison-table th,\n    .comparison-table td {\n        padding: 18px 20px;\n        text-align: left;\n        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n        vertical-align: top;\n    }\n    .comparison-table thead th {\n        background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        color: var(--header-text-color);\n        font-size: 18px;\n        font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .comparison-table thead th:first-child {\n        text-align: left;\n        background-color: #f7f7f7;\n    }\n    .comparison-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {\n        background-color: var(--background-alt);\n    }\n    .comparison-table tbody tr:last-child td {\n        border-bottom: none;\n    }\n    .comparison-table tbody td:first-child {\n        font-weight: bold;\n        color: var(--header-text-color);\n        width: 18%;\n    }\n    .comparison-table .product-title {\n        font-size: 1.1em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        display: block;\n        margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    .comparison-table .sub-text {\n        display: block;\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n        margin-top: 4px;\n        color: #555;\n    }\n    .comparison-table .nutrition-values span {\n        display: block;\n    }\n    .comparison-table .price-info {\n        font-size: 1.1em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        color: var(--header-text-color);\n    }\n    .comparison-table .icon-check { color: #28a745; font-weight: bold; }\n\n    @media (max-width: 900px) {\n        .comparison-table thead { display: none; }\n        .comparison-table, .comparison-table tbody, .comparison-table tr, .comparison-table td {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n        .comparison-table tr {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .comparison-table td {\n            text-align: right;\n            padding-left: 45%;\n            position: relative;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n        }\n        .comparison-table td:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        .comparison-table td:first-child {\n            width: 100%;\n            background-color: #f7f7f7;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 12px;\n        }\n        .comparison-table td::before {\n            content: attr(data-label);\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 15px;\n            left: 15px;\n            width: calc(45% - 30px);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: left;\n            white-space: normal;\n        }\n    }\n<\/style>\n<\/head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"comparison-container\">\n    <h2>Uitgebreide Vergelijking Energierepen<\/h2>\n    <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th>Kenmerk<\/th>\n                <th><span class=\"product-title\">Amacx Energy Oat Bar<\/span><\/th>\n                <th><span class=\"product-title\">Amacx Fruit Chew<\/span><\/th>\n                <th><span class=\"product-title\">Amacx Energy Nougat<\/span><\/th>\n                <th><span class=\"product-title\">Maurten Solid 160<\/span><\/th>\n            <\/tr>\n        <\/thead>\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Type Energie<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\"><strong>Langzaam & Geleidelijk<\/strong><span class=\"sub-text\">Op basis van complexe koolhydraten uit havermout voor stabiele energie.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\"><strong>Snel & Efficiënt<\/strong><span class=\"sub-text\">Dankzij de 2:1 ratio, vergelijkbaar met een gel maar dan kauwbaar.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\"><strong>Snel & Efficiënt<\/strong><span class=\"sub-text\">De 2:1 ratio zorgt voor een snelle opname van koolhydraten.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\"><strong>Snel & Efficiënt<\/strong><span class=\"sub-text\">Ontworpen voor snelle energie, maar als vaste voeding voor variatie.<\/span><\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Basis & Textuur<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\">Havermoutbasis<span class=\"sub-text\">Zachte, niet-droege reep die makkelijk eet en niet smelt.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\">Fruitpulp-basis<span class=\"sub-text\">Zachte, kauwbare 'gummy' textuur die niet plakt.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\">Nougat & Amandelbasis<span class=\"sub-text\">Klassieke, zachte nougat-textuur die licht verteerbaar is.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\">Haver- & Rijstbasis<span class=\"sub-text\">Stevige, compacte en kauwbare structuur.<\/span><\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n             <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Smaken<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\">Banana, Coconut, Lemon, Sweet Figs.<span class=\"sub-text\">(Lemon is op amandelbasis).<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\">Cassis, Orange, Piña (ananas).<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\">Cranberry, Papaya, Speculoos.<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\">Cacao, Citroen.<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Koolhydraten per Reep<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\">31.5 gram<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\">30 gram<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\">~32 gram<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\"><strong>40 gram<\/strong><\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Voedingswaarden<\/strong><span class=\"sub-text\">(per reep)<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\" class=\"nutrition-values\">\n                    <span><strong>Suikers:<\/strong> 7 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Vetten:<\/strong> 3.5 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Eiwitten:<\/strong> 6 g<\/span>\n                <\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\" class=\"nutrition-values\">\n                    <span><strong>Suikers:<\/strong> 28 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Vetten:<\/strong> &lt;0.2 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Eiwitten:<\/strong> &lt;0.2 g<\/span>\n                <\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\" class=\"nutrition-values\">\n                    <span><strong>Suikers:<\/strong> ~24 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Vetten:<\/strong> ~2.5 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Eiwitten:<\/strong> ~1.5 g<\/span>\n                <\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\" class=\"nutrition-values\">\n                    <span><strong>Suikers:<\/strong> 19.1 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Vetten:<\/strong> 3.2 g<\/span>\n                    <span><strong>Eiwitten:<\/strong> 2.6 g<\/span>\n                <\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Ideaal Gebruiksmoment<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\"><strong>Vóór inspanning<\/strong> of in de <strong>eerste uren<\/strong> van een lange, rustige training.<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\">Voor, tijdens en na. Ideaal als <strong>snel, kauwbaar alternatief<\/strong> voor een gel.<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\">Voor, tijdens en na. Perfect als <strong>smakelijke, vaste afwisseling<\/strong> op gels.<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\">Voor, tijdens (lage\/medium intensiteit) of na. Ideaal om <strong>vaste en vloeibare voeding af te wisselen<\/strong>.<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Belangrijkste Dieetinfo<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\">Bevat gluten (haver, tarwe). Lemon-variant is op amandelbasis.<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\"><span class=\"icon-check\"><\/span> <strong>Vegan, gluten- & lactosevrij.<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\">Gluten- & lactosevrij.<span class=\"sub-text\">Bevat noten (amandelen) en ei.<\/span><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\"><span class=\"icon-check\"><\/span> <strong>Vegan & glutenvrij.<\/strong><\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td data-label=\"Kenmerk\"><strong>Prijs per Stuk<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Oat Bar\" class=\"price-info\">€ 1,99<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Fruit Chew\" class=\"price-info\">€ 2,49<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Amacx Nougat\" class=\"price-info\">€ 2,20<\/td>\n                <td data-label=\"Maurten Solid 160\" class=\"price-info\">€ 2,95<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n        <\/tbody>\n    <\/table>\n<\/div>\n<\/body>\n<\/html>","text_alignment":"left","add_vertical_spacing":true,"add_horizontal_spacing":true}},"related-products":{"type":"related-products","blocks":{"section-header":{"type":"_section-header","static":true,"settings":{"subheading":"","title":"Favorieten van andere sporters:","content":"","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_style":"outline","text_alignment":"left","heading_size":"h3","title_icon":"none","show_scrolling_title":false},"blocks":{}}},"settings":{"color_scheme":"scheme-2","stack_products":true,"recommendations_count":4,"products_per_row_mobile":"1","products_per_row_desktop":4,"show_view_all_button":true,"show_scrolling_bar":true}}},"order":["main","custom_liquid_FGWnLa","custom_liquid_teda9d","related-products"]}